---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>
    <strong>Critter</strong> is a co-op multiplayer climbing exploration game built on
    Unreal Engine 5 and the Lyra sample project. You and a small group climb, scavenge,
    and survive across a stitched-together set of biomes — finding Rift Shards, completing
    missions, and unlocking new regions as you go.
  </p>
  <p>
    This devlog drops a single longer post each month covering what shipped, what broke,
    and what's coming next. Posts are written from the actual git history of the project,
    so the changelog is real, not aspirational.
  </p>
  <p>
    Built solo by <a href="https://github.com/NRG-Nad">NRG-Nad</a>. Source for the game is
    private; source for the devlog is
    <a href="https://github.com/NRG-Nad/critter-devlog">here</a>.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
